<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٤٩٦- الوَلِيد، الرَّمّاح.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعَ ابْن عَبّاس، ومُحَمد بْن عليٍّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">رَوَى عَنه:</span> جَعفر بْن بُرقان.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>